<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>
        <%= pageTitle %> - Medication Tracker
    </title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-indigo-100">
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>

        <main class="max-w-6xl mx-auto mt-10 px-4">
            <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-md p-8">
                <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Help Center</h1>

                <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-8">
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                        <div class="space-y-4">
                            <div class="border-b pb-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How do I add a new medication?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Click on the "Add Medication" button in the dashboard and fill
                                    in the required details about your medication.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-b pb-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">How do reminders work?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Reminders can be set when adding medications. You'll receive
                                    notifications through your preferred method (email/SMS).</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="border-b pb-4">
                                <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I share my medication schedule with my doctor?</h3>
                                <p class="text-gray-600">Yes, you can generate a report of your medication schedule and
                                    adherence to share with your healthcare provider.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="space-y-4">
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold">Need More Help?</h2>
                        <p class="text-gray-600">If you can't find the answer you're looking for, please reach out to
                            our support team:</p>
                        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-600">
                            <li>Email: anindyakanti2020@gmail.com</li>
                            <li>Phone: 1-800-MED-HELP</li>
                            <li>Hours: 24/7</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
</body>

</html>